r=0\">web search</a><div><div class=\"hover-container\"><form action=\"http://googlesearch.northwestern.edu/search\" id=\"web-search\" method=\"get\"><input name=\"site\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"mcc\"/><input name=\"client\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"mcc\"/><input name=\"output\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"xml_no_dtd\"/><input name=\"proxystylesheet\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"mcc2014\"/><input name=\"filter\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"0\"/><input autocomplete=\"off\" id=\"q\" name=\"q\" placeholder=\"Search this site\" type=\"search\"/></form></div></div></li><li id=\"top-nav-explore\"><a href=\"../../../explore/index.html\">Explore</a></li></ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h1 id=\"major-title\"><span class=\"header-container\"><a href=\"../../index.html\">Research and Faculty</a><span class=\"extraneous\">, McCormick School of Engineering, Northwestern University</span></span></h1>\r\n<div id=\"mobile-nav\">\r\n<div id=\"mobile-nav-handle\">\r\n<div id=\"inner\">SECTION MENU</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</header>\r\n<div id=\"container\">\r\n<div id=\"left-col\"><div id=\"section-nav-head\">IN THIS SECTION</div><nav><ul><li><a href=\"../../index.html\">Research and Faculty</a></li><li class=\"active expanded section\"><a href=\"../index.html\">Faculty Directory</a><ul><li class=\"index\"><a href=\"../index.html\">Faculty Directory</a></li><li><a href=\"../faculty-fellows.html\">Faculty Fellows</a></li></ul></li></ul></nav></div>\r\n<div id=\"main-content-wrap\">\r\n<div id=\"main-content\" role=\"main\"><h1 id=\"page-title\"><div>Faculty Directory</div>Randall Berry</h1><div id=\"faculty-profile-left\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"../../../images/research-and-faculty/directory/berry-randy.jpg\"/><p class=\"title\">Professor of Electrical Engineering and Computer Science</p><p class=\"title\">Lorraine Morton Professor</p><h2>Contact</h2>2145 Sheridan Road<br/>Tech Room M318<br/>Evanston, IL 60208-3109<br/><br/><a class=\"phone_link\" href=\"tel://847-491-7074\"><span class=\"phone_link_verbose\">847-491-7074</span></a><a class=\"mail_link\" href=\"mailto:rberry@eecs.northwestern.edu\">Email <span>Randall&#160;Berry</span></a><h2 class=\"sites-header\">Website</h2><p><a href=\"http://commnet.ece.northwestern.edu/\" target=\"_blank\">Communications Networking Lab</a></p><p><a href=\"http://users.eecs.northwestern.edu/~rberry/\" target=\"_blank\">Randall Berry's Homepage</a></p><hr/><h2>Departments</h2><p><a href=\"http://eecs.northwestern.edu\" target=\"_blank\">Electrical Engineering and Computer Science</a></p></div><div id=\"faculty-profile-right\"><h2>Education</h2><p>Ph.D. Electrical Engineering and Computer Science, MIT, Cambridge, MA</p>\r\n<p>S.M. Electrical Engineering and Computer Science, MIT, Cambridge, MA</p>\r\n<p>B.S. Electrical Engineering, University of Missouri, Rolla, MO</p><br/><h2>Research Interests</h2><p><p>Prof. Berry's research covers resource allocation problems that arise in networked systems ranging from communication networks to social networks. This work uses mathematical models to gain insights into such systems and draws on tools from stochastic modeling, optimization, economics and algorithms. Specific topics of current interest include developing distributed resource allocation technicques for wireless networks, dynamic spectrum sharing and wireless spectrum policy, understanding the role of incentives in network security and modeling learning and adoption in social networks.</p></p><br/><h2>Selected Publications</h2><ul><li>Cheng Chen, Randall A. Berry, Michael L. Honig, Vijay G. Subramanian, \"<em>The impact of small-cell bandwidth requirements on strategic operators</em>\", 2017 IEEE International Symposium on Dynamic Spectrum Access Networks, DySPAN 2017, (2017)</li><li>Arnob Ghosh, Saswati Sarkar, Randall Berry, \"<em>The Value of Side-Information in Secondary Spectrum Markets</em>\", IEEE Journal on Selected Areas in Communications, (2017)</li><li>Tho Ngoc Le, Vijay G. Subramanian, Randall A. Berry, \"<em>Quantifying the utility of imperfect reviews in stopping information cascades</em>\", 2016 IEEE 55th Conference on Decision and Control, CDC 2016, (2016)</li><li>Th&#157;nh Nguyen, Hang Zhou, Randall A. Berry, Michael L. Honig, Rakesh Vohra, \"<em>The cost of free spectrum</em>\", Operations Research, (2016)</li><li>Th&#157;nh Nguyen, Vijay Subramanian, Randall Berry, \"<em>Delay in Trade Networks</em>\", Operations Research, (2016)</li><li>Berry, Randall; Tirkkonen, Olav; Singh, Bikramjit; Hailu, Sofonias; Koufos, Konstantinos, \"<em>Coordination protocol for inter-operator spectrum sharing in co-primary 5G small cell networks</em>\", IEEE Communications Magazine, (2015)</li><li>Berry, Randall A.; Subramanian, Vijay G.; Le, Tho Ngoc, \"<em>The impact of observation and action errors on informational cascades</em>\", Proceedings of the IEEE Conference on Decision and Control, (2015)</li><li>Liu, Chang; Berry, Randall A., \"<em>Competition with shared spectrum</em>\", 2014 IEEE International Symposium on Dynamic Spectrum Access Networks, DYSPAN 2014, (2014)</li><li>Le, T.N.; Subramanian, V.G.; Berry, R.A., \"<em>The value of noise for informational cascades</em>\", IEEE International Symposium on Information Theory - Proceedings, (2014)</li><li>Nguyen, Thanh; Berry, Randall; Honig, Michael; Subramanian, Vijay; Vohra, Rakesh, \"<em>Market structures for wireless services with shared spectrum</em>\", 2013 51st Annual Allerton Conference on Communication, Control, and Computing, Allerton 2013, (2013)</li><li>Zhou, Hang; Berry, Randall; Honig, Michael L.; Vohra, Rakesh, \"<em>Complexity of allocation problems in spectrum markets with interference complementarities</em>\", IEEE Journal on Selected Areas in Communications, (2013)</li><li>Berry, Randall A., \"<em>Optimal power-delay tradeoffs in fading channels-small-delay asymptotics</em>\", IEEE Transactions on Information Theory, (2013)</li><li>Honig, Michael L.; Berry, Randall A.; Schmidt, David A.; Shi, Changxin; Utschick, Wolfgang, \"<em>Comparison of distributed beamforming algorithms for MIMO interference networks</em>\", IEEE Transactions on Signal Processing, (2013)</li><li>Randall Berry and Ramesh Johari, \"<em>Economic Modeling with Engineering Applications</em>\", NOW Publishers, (2013)</li><li>Berry, Randall A., \"<em>Network market design part II: Spectrum markets</em>\", IEEE Communications Magazine, (2012)</li><li>K. Huang, J. G. Andrews, D. Guo, R. W. Heath, Jr. and R. A. Berry, \"<em>Spatial Interference Cancellation for Multiantenna Mobile Ad Hoc Networks</em>\", Ieee Transactions on Information Theory, (2012)</li><li>Berry, R.A.; Zhou, H.; Nguyen, T.; Vohra, R.; Honig, M.L., \"<em>The impact of additional unlicensed spectrum on wireless services competition</em>\", New Frontiers in Dynamic Spectrum Access Networks (DySPAN), 2011 IEEE Symposium on, (2011)</li><li>R Berry;ML Honig;R Vohra, \"<em>Spectrum Markets: Motivation, Challenges, and Implications</em>\", Ieee Communications Magazine, (2010)</li><li>RA Berry, DNC Tse, \"<em>Shannon Meets Nash on the Interference Channel</em>\", Arxiv preprint arXiv:1007.1756, (2010)</li><li>VG SUBRAMANIAN;RA BERRY;R AGRAWAL, \"<em>Joint Scheduling and Resource Allocation in CDMA Systems</em>\", Ieee Transactions on Information Theory, (2010)</li><li>C MILLING;S SUBRAMANIAN;S SHAKKOTTAI;R BERRY, \"<em>Routing over Multi-hop Wireless Networks With Non-ergodic Mobility</em>\", Ieee Infocom 2009 - Ieee Conference on Computer Communications, Vols 1-5, (2009)</li><li>RA BERRY;DNC TSE, \"<em>Information Theory Meets Game Theory on The Interference Channel</em>\", Itw: 2009 Ieee Information Theory Workshop on Networking and Information Theory, (2009)</li><li>JW HUANG, VG SUBRAMANIAN, R AGRAWAL, et al., \"<em>Joint Scheduling and Resource Allocation in Uplink OFDM Systems for Broadband Wireless Access Networks</em>\", IEEE JOURNAL ON SELECTED AREAS IN COMMUNICATIONS, (2009)</li><li>DA SCHMIDT, CX SHI, RA BERRY, ML HONIG, W UTSCHICK, \"<em>Distributed Resource Allocation Schemes</em>\", IEEE SIGNAL PROCESSING MAGAZINE, (2009)</li><li>YE SAGDUYU, DN GUO, R BERRY, \"<em>On the delay and throughput of digital and analog network coding for wireless broadcast</em>\", 42nd Annual Conference on Information Sciences and Systems, (2008)</li><li>J ANDREWS, S SHAKKOTTAI, R HEATH, et al., \"<em>Rethinking Information Theory for Mobile Ad Hoc Networks</em>\", IEEE COMMUNICATIONS MAGAZINE, (2008)</li><li>R BERRY, D TSE, \"<em>Information Theoretic Games on Interference Channels</em>\", IEEE International Symposium on Information Theory, (2008)</li><li>J Bae, E Beigman, RA Berry, ML Honig, R ..., \"<em>Sequential bandwidth and power auctions for distributed spectrum sharing</em>\", IEEE Journal on Selected Areas in Communications, (2008)</li><li>J Bae, E Beigman, R Berry, ML Honig, H Shen ..., \"<em>Spectrum Markets for Wireless Services</em>\", Proceedings of the 2008 IEEE Symposium on New Frontiers in Dynamic Spectrum Access Networks\t, (2008)</li></ul></div><div style=\"clear: both;\">&#160;</div></div>\r\n  \r\n<div id=\"back-to-top\"><a href=\"#top\">BACK TO TOP</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<footer class=\"cf\" role=\"contentinfo\"><div class=\"header-container cf\"><a href=\"http://www.northwestern.edu\" id=\"footer-logo\" target=\"_blank\">Northwestern Seal</a><div id=\"footer-links\"><p><span class=\"footer-branding-element\">McCormick School of Engineering,</span>&#160;\r\n                        \r\n                        \r\n                        <span class=\"footer-branding-element\">Northwestern University</span></p><address>Technological Institute, 2145 Sheridan Road, Evanston, IL 60208</address><p class=\"contact-info white-single-arrow\"><a href=\"../../../contact/index.html\">view all contact info</a></p><ul><li><a href=\"../../../academics/apply.html\">Admissions</a></li><li><a href=\"../index.html\">Faculty Directory</a></li><li><a href=\"http://giving.northwestern.edu/node/2668\" target=\