=mcc2014&amp;filter=0\">web search</a><div><div class=\"hover-container\"><form action=\"http://googlesearch.northwestern.edu/search\" id=\"web-search\" method=\"get\"><input name=\"site\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"mcc\"/><input name=\"client\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"mcc\"/><input name=\"output\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"xml_no_dtd\"/><input name=\"proxystylesheet\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"mcc2014\"/><input name=\"filter\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"0\"/><input autocomplete=\"off\" id=\"q\" name=\"q\" placeholder=\"Search this site\" type=\"search\"/></form></div></div></li><li id=\"top-nav-explore\"><a href=\"../../../explore/index.html\">Explore</a></li></ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h1 id=\"major-title\"><span class=\"header-container\"><a href=\"../../index.html\">Research and Faculty</a><span class=\"extraneous\">, McCormick School of Engineering, Northwestern University</span></span></h1>\r\n<div id=\"mobile-nav\">\r\n<div id=\"mobile-nav-handle\">\r\n<div id=\"inner\">SECTION MENU</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</header>\r\n<div id=\"container\">\r\n<div id=\"left-col\"><div id=\"section-nav-head\">IN THIS SECTION</div><nav><ul><li><a href=\"../../index.html\">Research and Faculty</a></li><li class=\"active expanded section\"><a href=\"../index.html\">Faculty Directory</a><ul><li class=\"index\"><a href=\"../index.html\">Faculty Directory</a></li><li><a href=\"../faculty-fellows.html\">Faculty Fellows</a></li></ul></li></ul></nav></div>\r\n<div id=\"main-content-wrap\">\r\n<div id=\"main-content\" role=\"main\"><h1 id=\"page-title\"><div>Faculty Directory</div>Alok Choudhary</h1><div id=\"faculty-profile-left\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"../../../images/research-and-faculty/directory/choudhary-alok.jpg\"/><p class=\"title\">Henry and Isabelle Dever Professor of Electrical Engineering and Computer Science</p><h2>Contact</h2>2145 Sheridan Road<br/>Tech Room L469<br/>Evanston, IL 60208-3109<br/><br/><a class=\"phone_link\" href=\"tel://847-467-4129\"><span class=\"phone_link_verbose\">847-467-4129</span></a><a class=\"mail_link\" href=\"mailto:a-choudhary@northwestern.edu\">Email <span>Alok&#160;Choudhary</span></a><h2 class=\"sites-header\">Website</h2><p><a href=\"http://www.eecs.northwestern.edu/~choudhar/\" target=\"_blank\">Alok Choudhary's Homepage</a></p><p><a href=\"http://cucis.ece.northwestern.edu/\" target=\"_blank\">Center for Ultra-scale Computing and Information Security (CUCIS)</a></p><hr/><h2>Departments</h2><p><a href=\"http://eecs.northwestern.edu\" target=\"_blank\">Electrical Engineering and Computer Science</a></p><hr/><p><a href=\"http://mccormick.northwestern.edu/docs/public_cv/Choudhary-Alok-CV.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Download CV</a></p></div><div id=\"faculty-profile-right\"><h2>Education</h2><p>Ph.D. Computer Engineering, University of Illinois, Urbana-Champaign, IL</p>\r\n<p>M.S. Computer Engineering, University of Massachusetts, Amherst, MA</p>\r\n<p>B.E. (Hons) Electrical and Electronics Engineering, Birla Institute of Technology and Science, Pilani, India</p><br/><h2>Research Interests</h2><p><p>High-performance computing; data intensive computing; scalable data mining; computer architecture; high-performance I/O systems and software; Social Media, Materials and Medical Informatics</p></p><br/><h2>Selected Publications</h2><ul><li>Jianwei Liao, Balazs Gerofi, Guo Yuan Lien, Takemasa Miyoshi, Seiya Nishizawa, Hirofumi Tomita, Wei Keng Liao, Alok Choudhary, Yutaka Ishikawa, \"<em>A flexible I/O arbitration framework for netCDF-based big data processing workflows on high-end supercomputers</em>\", Concurrency Computation Practice and Experience, (2017)</li><li>Adam G. Gagorik, Brett Savoie, Nick Jackson, Ankit Agrawal, Alok Choudhary, Mark A. Ratner, George C. Schatz, Kevin L. Kohlstedt, \"<em>Improved Scaling of Molecular Network Calculations</em>\", Journal of Physical Chemistry Letters, (2017)</li><li>Yusheng Xie, Zhengzhang Chen, Diana Palsetia, Goce Trajcevski, Ankit Agrawal, Alok Choudhary, \"<em>SILVERBACK+</em>\", Knowledge and Information Systems, (2017)</li><li>Logan Ward, Ruoqian Liu, Amar Krishna, Vinay I. Hegde, Ankit Agrawal, Alok Choudhary, Chris Wolverton, \"<em>Including crystal structure attributes in machine learning models of formation energies via Voronoi tessellations</em>\", Physical Review B, (2017)</li><li>Ankit Agrawal, Bryce Meredig, Chris Wolverton, Alok Choudhary, \"<em>A Formation Energy Predictor for Crystalline Materials Using Ensemble Data Mining</em>\", Proceedings - 16th IEEE International Conference on Data Mining Workshops, ICDMW 2016, (2017)</li><li>Ankit Agrawal, Jason Mathias, David Baker, Alok Choudhary, \"<em>Five Year Life Expectancy Calculator for Older Adults</em>\", Proceedings - 16th IEEE International Conference on Data Mining Workshops, ICDMW 2016, (2017)</li><li>Amar Krishna, Ankit Agrawal, Alok Choudhary, \"<em>Predicting the Outcome of Startups</em>\", Proceedings - 16th IEEE International Conference on Data Mining Workshops, ICDMW 2016, (2017)</li><li>Sunwoo Lee, Wei Keng Liao, Ankit Agrawal, Nikos Hardavellas, Alok Choudhary, \"<em>Evaluation of K-means data clustering algorithm on Intel Xeon Phi</em>\", Proceedings - 2016 IEEE International Conference on Big Data, Big Data 2016, (2017)</li></ul></div><div style=\"clear: both;\">&#160;</div></div>\r\n  \r\n<div id=\"back-to-top\"><a href=\"#top\">BACK TO TOP</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<footer class=\"cf\" role=\"contentinfo\"><div class=\"header-container cf\"><a href=\"http://www.northwestern.edu\" id=\"footer-logo\" target=\"_blank\">Northwestern Seal</a><div id=\"footer-links\"><p><span class=\"footer-branding-element\">McCormick School of Engineering,</span>&#160;\r\n                        \r\n                        \r\n                        <span class=\"footer-branding-element\">Northwestern University</span></p><address>Technological Institute, 2145 Sheridan Road, Evanston, IL 60208</address><p class=\"contact-info white-single-arrow\"><a href=\"../../