ader\">Website</h2><p><a href=\"http://users.eecs.northwestern.edu/~chrdimo/\" target=\"_blank\"> Christos Dimoulas' Homepage</a></p><hr/><h2>Departments</h2><p><a href=\"http://eecs.northwestern.edu\" target=\"_blank\">Electrical Engineering and Computer Science</a></p></div><div id=\"faculty-profile-right\"><h2>Education</h2><p>Ph.D. in <span>Computer Science</span>, <span><span></span></span>Northeastern University, <span class=\"_Xbe\">Boston, MA</span></p><br/><h2>Research Interests</h2><p>I am interested in the design and semantics of programming languages. More specifically, my goal is to develop programming languages technology that facilitates the construction of secure and robust component-based software systems.</p><br/></div><div style=\"clear: both;\">&#160;</div></div>\r\n  \r\n<div id=\"back-to-top\"><a href=\"#top\">BACK TO TOP</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<footer class=\"cf\" role=\"contentinfo\"><div class=\"header-container cf\"><a href=\"http://www.northwestern.edu\" id=\"footer-logo\" target=\"_blank\">Northwestern Seal</a><div id=\"footer-links\"><p><span class=\"footer-branding-element\">McCormick School of Engineering,</span>&#160;\r\n                        \r\n                        \r\n                        <span class=\"footer-branding-element\">Northwestern University</span></p><address>Technological Institute, 2145 Sheridan Road, Evanston, IL 60208</address><p class=\"contact-info white-single-arrow\"><a href=\"../../../contact/index.html\">view all contact info</a></p><ul><li><a href=\"../../../academics/apply.html\">Admissions</a></li><li><a href=\"../index.html\">Faculty Directory</a></li><li><a href=\"http://giving.northwestern.edu/node/2668\" target=\"_blank\">Give to McCormick</a></li><li><a href=\"../../../contact/maps.html\">Tech Room Finder / Maps</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.mccormick.northwestern.edu/faculty-staff-resources/safety-emergency-information/index.html\">Emergency Information</a></li><li><a href=\"http:/