2008)</li></ul></div><div style=\"clear: both;\">&#160;</div></div>\r\n  \r\n<div id=\"back-to-top\"><a href=\"#top\">BACK TO TOP</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<footer class=\"cf\" role=\"contentinfo\"><div class=\"header-container cf\"><a href=\"http://www.northwestern.edu\" id=\"footer-logo\" target=\"_blank\">Northwestern Seal</a><div id=\"footer-links\"><p><span class=\"footer-branding-element\">McCormick School of Engineering,</span>&#160;\r\n                        \r\n                        \r\n                        <span class=\"footer-branding-element\">Northwestern University</span></p><address>Technological Institute, 2145 Sheridan Road, Evanston, IL 60208</address><p class=\"contact-info white-single-arrow\"><a href=\"../../../contact/index.html\">view all contact info</a></p><ul><li><a href=\"../../../academics/apply.html\">Admissions</a></li><li><a href=\"../index.html\">Faculty Directory</a></li><li><a href=\"http://giving.northwestern.edu/node/2668\" target=\"_blank\">Give to McCormick</a></li><li><a href=\"../../../contact/maps.html\">Tech Room Finder / Maps</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.mccormick.northwestern.edu/faculty-staff-resources/safety-emergency-information/index.html\">Emergency Information</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.northwestern.edu\" target=\"_blank\">Northwestern Home</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.mccormick.northwestern.edu/offices-services/index.html#lost-and-found\" target=\"_blank\">Tech Lost and Found</a></li></ul></div><div id=\"footer-icons\"><div id=\"footer-icon-set1\"><a class=\"icon-twitter iconset-footer\" href=\"http://twitter.com/NorthwesternEng\" target=\"_blank\">McCormick on twitter</a><a class=\"icon-facebook iconset-footer\" href=\"http://facebook.com/northwesternengineering\" target=\"_blank\">McCormick on facebook</a><a class=\"icon-google iconset-footer\" href=\"https://plus.google.com/112338659769568952865/posts\" target=\"_blank\">McCormick on google</a></div><div id=\"footer-icon-set2\"><a class