ut name=\"site\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"mcc\"/><input name=\"client\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"mcc\"/><input name=\"output\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"xml_no_dtd\"/><input name=\"proxystylesheet\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"mcc2014\"/><input name=\"filter\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"0\"/><input autocomplete=\"off\" id=\"q\" name=\"q\" placeholder=\"Search this site\" type=\"search\"/></form></div></div></li><li id=\"top-nav-explore\"><a href=\"../../../explore/index.html\">Explore</a></li></ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h1 id=\"major-title\"><span class=\"header-container\"><a href=\"../../index.html\">Research and Faculty</a><span class=\"extraneous\">, McCormick School of Engineering, Northwestern University</span></span></h1>\r\n<div id=\"mobile-nav\">\r\n<div id=\"mobile-nav-handle\">\r\n<div id=\"inner\">SECTION MENU</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</header>\r\n<div id=\"container\">\r\n<div id=\"left-col\"><div id=\"section-nav-head\">IN THIS SECTION</div><nav><ul><li><a href=\"../../index.html\">Research and Faculty</a></li><li class=\"active expanded section\"><a href=\"../index.html\">Faculty Directory</a><ul><li class=\"index\"><a href=\"../index.html\">Faculty Directory</a></li><li><a href=\"../faculty-fellows.html\">Faculty Fellows</a></li></ul></li></ul></nav></div>\r\n<div id=\"main-content-wrap\">\r\n<div id=\"main-content\" role=\"main\"><h1 id=\"page-title\"><div>Faculty Directory</div>Dongning Guo</h1><div id=\"faculty-profile-left\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"../../../images/research-and-faculty/directory/guo-dongning.jpg\"/><p class=\"title\">Professor of Electrical Engineering and Computer Science</p><h2>Contact</h2>2145 Sheridan Road<br/>Tech Room L393<br/>Evanston, IL 60208-3109<br/><br/><a class=\"phone_link\" href=\"tel://847-491-3056\"><span class=\"phone_link_verbose\">847-491-3056</span></a><a class=\"mail_link\" href=\"mailto:dguo@northwestern.edu\">Email <span>Dongning&#160;Guo</span></a><h2 class=\"sites-header\">Website</h2><p><a href=\"http://users.eecs.northwestern.edu/~dguo/\" target=\"_blank\">Dongning Guo's Homepage</a></p><p><a href=\"http://commnet.eecs.northwestern.edu/\" target=\"_blank\">Communications and Networking Laboratory</a></p><hr/><h2>Departments</h2><p><a href=\"http://eecs.northwestern.edu\" target=\"_blank\">Electrical Engineering and Computer Science</a></p><hr/><p><a href=\"http://mccormick.northwestern.edu/docs/public_cv/Guo-Dongning-CV.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Download CV</a></p></div><div id=\"faculty-profile-right\"><h2>Education</h2><p>Ph.D. Electrical Engineering, Princeton University, Princeton, NJ</p>\r\n<p>M.A. Electrical Engineering, Princeton University, Princeton, NJ</p>\r\n<p>M.Eng. Electrical Engineering, National University of Singapore, Singapore</p>\r\n<p>B.Eng. Electrical Engineering &amp; Information Science, University of Science &amp; Technology of China, Hefei, China</p><br/><h2>Research Interests</h2><p><p><span>My research interests lie in communications, networking, information theory, and signal processing.  My current projects concern next generation cellular networks, the Internet of Things, information theory of many-user systems, millimeter wave and full-duplex communication, as well as experimentation using software-defined radios.</span></p></p><br/><h2>Selected Publications</h2><ul><li>Fei Teng, Dongning Guo, Michael L. Honig, \"<em>Sharing of Unlicensed Spectrum by Strategic Operators</em>\", IEEE Journal on Selected Areas in Communications, (2017)</li><li>Zhiyi Zhou, Dongning Guo, Michael L. Honig, \"<em>Licensed and Unlicensed Spectrum Allocation in Heterogeneous Networks</em>\", IEEE Transactions on Communications, (2017)</li><li>Xu Chen, Tsung Yi Chen, Dongning Guo, \"<em>Capacity of Gaussian Many-Access Channels</em>\", IEEE Transactions on Information Theory, (2017)</li><li>Zhiyi Zhou, Dongning Guo, Michael L. Honig, \"<em>Allocation of licensed and unlicensed spectrum in heterogeneous networks</em>\", 2016 Australian Communications Theory Workshop, AusCTW 2016, (2016)</li><li>X. Chen and D. Guo, \"<em>Wireless Public Safety Networks (D. Camara and N. Nikaein, eds.), vol. 2: A Systematic Approach</em>\", Elsevier, (2016)</li><li>Binnan Zhuang, Dongning Guo, Michael L. Honig, \"<em>Traffic-Driven Spectrum Allocation in Heterogeneous Networks</em>\", IEEE Journal on Selected Areas in Communications, (2015)</li><li>Mingguang Xu, Dongning Guo, Michael L. Honig, \"<em>Distributed Bi-Directional Training of Nonlinear Precoders and Receivers in Cellular Networks</em>\", IEEE Transactions on Signal Processing, (2015)</li><li>Guo, Dongning; Sabharwal, Ashutosh; Schniter, Philip; Bliss, Daniel W.; Rangarajan, Sampath, \"<em>In-band full-duplex wireless: Challenges and opportunities</em>\", IEEE Journal on Selected Areas in Communications, (2014)</li><li>Guo, Dongning; Zhang, Lei, \"<em>Virtual full duplex wireless broadcasting via compressed sensing</em>\", IEEE/ACM Transactions on Networking, (2014)</li><li>Chen, X.; Guo, D., \"<em>Many-access channels: The Gaussian case with random user activities</em>\", IEEE International Symposium on Information Theory - Proceedings, (2014)</li><li>Zhang, Lei; Li, Hui; Guo, Dongning, \"<em>Capacity of Gaussian channels with duty cycle and power constraints</em>\", IEEE Transactions on Information Theory, (2014)</li><li>Guo, Dongning; Taborda, Camilo G.; Perez-Cruz, Fernando, \"<em>Information-estimation relationships over binomial and negative binomial models</em>\", IEEE Transactions on Information Theory, (2014)</li><li>Zhang, Lei; Guo, Dongning, \"<em>Virtual Full Duplex Wireless Broadcasting via Compressed Sensing</em>\", IEEE/ACM Transactions on Networking, (2013)</li><li>, \"<em>The Interplay Between Information and Estimation Measures</em>\", now Publishers, (2013)</li><li>Berry, Randall A.; Sagduyu, Yalin E.; Guo, Dongning, \"<em>Throughput and stability for relay-assisted wireless broadcast with network coding</em>\", IEEE Journal on Selected Areas in Communications, (2013)</li><li>Honig, Michael L.; Guo, Dongning; Agarwal, Manish, \"<em>Error exponent for gaussian channels with partial sequential feedback</em>\", IEEE Transactions on Information Theory, (2013)</li><li>Honig, Michael L.; Guo, Dongning; Xu, Mingguang, \"<em>Multicarrier beamforming with limited feedback: A rate distortion approach</em>\", IEEE Transactions on Information Theory, (2013)</li><li>Honig, Michael L.; Guo, Dongning; Xu, Mingguang, \"<em>Downlink Noncoherent Cooperation without Transmitter Phase Alignment</em>\", IEEE Transactions on Wireless Communications, (2013)</li><li>D. Guo, S. Shamai (Shitz), and S. VerdA'u, \"<em>The Interplay between Information and Estimation Measures. Foundations and Trends in Signal Processing</em>\", NOW, (2013)</li><li>Guo, Dongning; Zhang, Lei; Luo, Jun, \"<em>Neighbor discovery for wireless networks via compressed sensing</em>\", Performance Evaluation, (2013)</li><li>K. Huang, J. G. Andrews, D. Guo, R. W. Heath, Jr. and R. A. Berry, \"<em>Spatial Interference Cancellation for Multiantenna Mobile Ad Hoc Networks</em>\", Ieee Transactions on Information Theory, (2012)</li><li>Y. Zhu and D. Guo, \"<em>The Degrees of Freedom of Isotropic MIMO Interference Channels Without State Information at the Transmitters</em>\", Ieee Transactions on Information Theory, (2012)</li><li>Y. Wu, D. Guo and S. Verdu, \"<em>Derivative of Mutual Information at Zero SNR: The Gaussian-Noise Case</em>\", Ieee Transactions on Information Theory, (2011)</li><li>Y Zhu;DN Guo, \"<em>Ergodic Fading Z-Interference Channels Without State Information at Transmitters</em>\", Ieee Transactions on Information Theory, (2011)</li><li>J Luo, D Guo, \"<em>Compressed neighbor discovery for wireless ad hoc networks: the Rayleigh fading case</em>\", ??_ , Control, and Computing, 2009. Allerton 2009. ??_, (2010)</li><li>Y Zhu, D Guo, \"<em>The Degrees of Freedom of MIMO Interference Channels without State Information at Transmitters</em>\", Arxiv preprint arXiv:1008.5196, (2010)</li><li>KH Hui, D Guo, RA Berry, \"<em>Medium access control via nearest-neighbor interactions for regular wireless networks</em>\", eecs.northwestern.edu, (2010)</li><li>D Guo, D Baron, S Shamai..., \"<em>A single-letter characterization of optimal noisy compressed sensing</em>\", Citeseer, (2009)</li><li>J Luo, D Guo, \"<em>On the entropy rate of hidden Markov processes observed through arbitrary memoryless channels</em>\", Information Theory, IEEE Transactions on, (2009)</li><li>M Agarwal, D Guo, M Honig, \"<em>Limited-Rate Channel State Feedback for Multicarrier Block Fading Channels</em>\", Submitted to IEEE Transactions on Information Theory, (2009)</li><li>J ANDREWS, S SHAKKOTTAI, R HEATH, et al., \"<em>Rethinking Information Theory for Mobile Ad Hoc Networks</em>\", IEEE COMMUNICATIONS MAGAZINE, (2008)</li><li>D Guo, S Shamai, S Verdu, \"<em>Estimation in Gaussian Noise: Properties of the Minimum Mean-square Error</em>\", Submitted to IEEE Trans. on Information Theory, (2008)</li><li>Dongning, Guo; Chih-Chun, Wang, \"<em>Multiuser detection of sparsely spread CDMA.</em>\", IEEE Journal on Selected Areas in Communications, (2008)</li><li>Dongning, Guo; Shamai, S.; Verdu, S., \"<em>Mutual information and conditional mean estimation in Poisson channels.</em>\", IEEE Transactions on Information Theory, (2008)</li></ul></div><div style=\"clear: both;\">&#160;</div></div>\r\n  \r\n<div id=\"back-to-top\"><a href=\"#top\">BACK TO TOP</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<footer class=\"cf\" role=\"contentinfo\"><div class=\"header-container cf\"><a href=\"http://www.northwestern.edu\" id=\"footer-logo\" target=\"_blank\">Northwestern Seal</a><div id=\"footer-links\"><p><span class=\"footer-branding-element\">McCormick School of Engineering,</span>&#160;\r\n                        \r\n                        \r\n                        <span class=\"footer-branding-element\">Northwestern University</span></p><address>Technological Institute, 2145 Sheridan Road, E