\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.computerworld.com/article/2982482/emerging-technology/why-artificial-intelligence-is-succeeding-then-and-now.html\">Why Artificial Intelligence is Succeeding: Then and Now</a></em></p>\r\n<p>Computer World</p>\r\n<p>September 12, 2015</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.computerworld.com/article/2936142/emerging-technology/how-artificial-intelligence-explains-analytics.html\">How Artificial Intelligence Explains Analytics</a></em></p>\r\n<p>Computer World</p>\r\n<p>June 19, 2015</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.computerworld.com/article/2918161/emerging-technology/the-ai-ecosystem.html\">The A.I. Ecosystem</a></em></p>\r\n<p>Computer World</p>\r\n<p>May 11, 2015</p></ul></div><div style=\"clear: both;\">&#160;</div></div>\r\n  \r\n<div id=\"back-to-top\"><a href=\"#top\">BACK TO TOP</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<footer class=\"cf\" role=\"contentinfo\"><div class=\"header-container cf\"><a href=\"http://www.northwestern.edu\" id=\"footer-logo\" target=\"_blank\">Northwestern Seal</a><div id=\"footer-links\"><p><span class=\"footer-branding-element\">McCormick School of Engineering,</span>&#160;\r\n                        \r\n                        \r\n                        <span class=\"footer-branding-element\">Northwestern University</span></p><address>Technological Institute, 2145 Sheridan Road, Evanston, IL 60208</address><p class=\"contact-info white-single-arrow\"><a href=\"../../../contact/index.html\">view all contact info</a></p><ul><li><a href=\"../../../academics/apply.html\">Admissions</a></li><li><a href=\"../index.html\">Faculty Directory</a></li><li><a href=\"http://giving.northwestern.edu/node/2668\" target=\"_blank\">Give to McCormick</a></li><li><a href=\"../../../contact/maps.html\">Tech Room Finder / Maps</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.mccormick.northwestern.edu/faculty-staff-resources/safety-emergency-information/index.html\">Emergency Information</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www