-3109<br/><br/><a class=\"phone_link\" href=\"tel://847-491-7164\"><span class=\"phone_link_verbose\">847-491-7164</span></a><a class=\"mail_link\" href=\"mailto:aggk@eecs.northwestern.edu\">Email <span>Aggelos&#160;Katsaggelos</span></a><h2 class=\"sites-header\">Website</h2><p><a href=\"http://ivpl.eecs.northwestern.edu/users/akatsaggelos\" target=\"_blank\">Aggelos Katsaggelos' Homepage</a></p><p><a href=\"http://ivpl.eecs.northwestern.edu/\" target=\"_blank\">Image and Video Processing Lab</a></p><hr/><h2>Departments</h2><p><a href=\"http://eecs.northwestern.edu\" target=\"_blank\">Electrical Engineering and Computer Science</a></p><h2>Affiliations</h2><p><a href=\"http://robotics.northwestern.edu\" target=\"_blank\">Master of Science in Robotics Program</a></p></div><div id=\"faculty-profile-right\"><h2>Education</h2><p>Ph.D. Electrical Engineering, Georgia Institute of Technology, Atlanta, GA</p>\r\n<p>M.S. Electrical Engineering, Georgia Institute of Technology, Atlanta, GA</p>\r\n<p>B.S. Electrical and Mechanical Engineering, Aristotelian University of Thessaloniki, Thessaloniki, Greece</p><br/><h2>Research Interests</h2><p><p>Multimedia signal processing; multimedia communications; computer vision; pattern recognition; DNA signal processing</p></p><br/><h2>Selected Publications</h2><ul><li>Oliver Cossairt, Xiang Huang, Nathan Matsuda, Harriet Stratis, Mary Broadway, Jack Tumblin, Greg Bearman, Eric Doehne, Aggelos Katsaggelos, Marc Walton, \"<em>Surface shape studies of the art of Paul Gauguin</em>\", 2015 Digital Heritage International Congress, Digital Heritage 2015, (2016)</li><li>, \"<em>Machine Learning Refined: Foundations, Algorithms, and Applications</em>\", Cambridge University Press, (2016)</li><li>Z. Chen, R. Molina, and A. K. Katsaggelos, \"<em>Handbook of Robust Low-Rank and Sparse Matrix Decomposition</em>\", CRC Press, (2016)</li><li>Wael AlSaafin, Salvador Villena, Miguel Vega, Rafael Molina, Aggelos K. Katsaggelos, \"<em>Compressive sensing super resolution from multiple observations with application to passive millimeter wave images</em>\", Digital Signal Processing: A Review Journal, (2016)</li><li>Pablo Ruiz, Rafael Molina, Aggelos K. Katsaggelos, \"<em>Joint data filtering and labeling using Gaussian processes and alternating direction method of multipliers</em>\", IEEE Transactions on Image Processing, (2016)</li><li>Morteza Zabihi, Serkan Kiranyaz, Ali Bahrami Rad, Aggelos K. Katsaggelos, Moncef Gabbouj, Turker Ince, \"<em>Analysis of High-Dimensional Phase Space via Poincar&#157; Section for Patient-Specific Seizure Detection</em>\", IEEE Transactions on Neural Systems and Rehabilitation Engineering, (2016)</li><li>Ali Bahrami Rad, Kjersti Engan, Aggelos K. Katsaggelos, Jan Terje Kval&#157;y, Lars Wik, Jo Kramer-Johansen, Unai Irusta, Trygve Eftest&#157;, \"<em>Automatic cardiac rhythm interpretation during resuscitation</em>\", Resuscitation, (2016)</li><li>Nicol&#157;s Pel&#157;ez, Arnau Gavalda-Miralles, Bao Wang, Heliodoro Tejedor Navarro, Herman Gudjonson, Ilaria Rebay, Aaron R. Dinner, Aggelos K. Katsaggelos, Lu&#157;s A N Amaral, Richard W. Carthew, \"<em>Dynamics and heterogeneity of a fate determinant during transition towards cell differentiation</em>\", eLife, (2015)</li><li>Xu Zhou, Javier Mateos, Fugen Zhou, Rafael Molina, Aggelos K. Katsaggelos, \"<em>Variational Dirichlet Blur Kernel Estimation</em>\", IEEE Transactions on Image Processing, (2015)</li><li>Matthew Woods, Aggelos K. Katsaggelos, \"<em>Spatial-Frequency-Based metric for image superresolution</em>\", Journal of the Optical Society of America A: Optics and Image Science, and Vision, (2015)</li><li>Katsaggelos, Aggelos K.; Kotu, Lasya Priya; Engan, Kjersti; Borhani, Reza; &#157;&#157;rn, Stein, \"<em>Cardiac magnetic resonance image-based classification of the risk of arrhythmias in post-myocardial infarction patients</em>\", Artificial Intelligence in Medicine, (2015)</li><li>Katsaggelos, Aggelos K.; Molina, Rafael; Ruiz, Pablo; Zhou, Xu; Mateos, Javier, \"<em>Variational Bayesian Blind Image Deconvolution: A review</em>\", Digital Signal Processing: A Review Journal, (2015)</li><li>Katsaggelos, Aggelos K.; Tsiligianni, Evaggelia; Kondi, Lisimachos P., \"<em>Preconditioning for underdetermined linear systems with sparse solutions</em>\", IEEE Signal Processing Letters, (2015)</li><li>Katsaggelos, Aggelos K.; Chen, Zhaofu; Molina, Rafael, \"<em>Robust Recovery of Temporally Smooth Signals from Under-Determined Multiple Measurements</em>\", IEEE Transactions on Signal Processing, (2015)</li><li>Katsaggelos, Aggelos K.; Molina, Rafael; Bahaadini, Sara, \"<em>Audiovisual Fusion: Challenges and New Approaches</em>\", Proceedings of the IEEE, (2015)</li><li>Katsaggelos, Aggelos K.; Molina, Rafael; Song, Lei; Jiang, Fan; Shi, Zhongke, \"<em>Toward dynamic scene understanding by hierarchical motion pattern mining</em>\", IEEE Transactions on Intelligent Transportation Systems, (2014)</li><li>Molina, R.; Vega, M.; Villena, S.; Katsaggelos, A.K., \"<em>A non-stationary image prior combination in super-resolution</em>\", Digital Signal Processing: A Review Journal, (2014)</li><li>Katsaggelos, Aggelos K.; Molina, Rafael; Derin Babacan, S.; Luessi, Martin; Booth, James R., \"<em>Variational Bayesian causal connectivity analysis for fMRI</em>\", Frontiers in Neuroinformatics, (2014)</li><li>Katsaggelos, Aggelos K.; Molina, Rafael; Ruiz, Pablo; Mateos, Javier; Camps-Valls, Gustavo, \"<em>Bayesian active remote sensing image classification</em>\", IEEE Transactions on Geoscience and Remote Sensing, (2014)</li><li>Katsaggelos, Aggelos K.; Kondi, Lisimachos P.; Tsiligianni, Evaggelia V., \"<em>Construction of incoherent unit norm tight frames with application to compressed sensing</em>\", IEEE Transactions on Information Theory, (2014)</li><li>Katsaggelos, Aggelos K.; Molina, Rafael; Babacan, S. Derin; Chen, Zhaofu, \"<em>Variational bayesian methods for multimedia problems</em>\", IEEE Transacti