web search</a><div><div class=\"hover-container\"><form action=\"http://googlesearch.northwestern.edu/search\" id=\"web-search\" method=\"get\"><input name=\"site\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"mcc\"/><input name=\"client\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"mcc\"/><input name=\"output\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"xml_no_dtd\"/><input name=\"proxystylesheet\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"mcc2014\"/><input name=\"filter\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"0\"/><input autocomplete=\"off\" id=\"q\" name=\"q\" placeholder=\"Search this site\" type=\"search\"/></form></div></div></li><li id=\"top-nav-explore\"><a href=\"../../../explore/index.html\">Explore</a></li></ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h1 id=\"major-title\"><span class=\"header-container\"><a href=\"../../index.html\">Research and Faculty</a><span class=\"extraneous\">, McCormick School of Engineering, Northwestern University</span></span></h1>\r\n<div id=\"mobile-nav\">\r\n<div id=\"mobile-nav-handle\">\r\n<div id=\"inner\">SECTION MENU</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</header>\r\n<div id=\"container\">\r\n<div id=\"left-col\"><div id=\"section-nav-head\">IN THIS SECTION</div><nav><ul><li><a href=\"../../index.html\">Research and Faculty</a></li><li class=\"active expanded section\"><a href=\"../index.html\">Faculty Directory</a><ul><li class=\"index\"><a href=\"../index.html\">Faculty Directory</a></li><li><a href=\"../faculty-fellows.html\">Faculty Fellows</a></li></ul></li></ul></nav></div>\r\n<div id=\"main-content-wrap\">\r\n<div id=\"main-content\" role=\"main\"><h1 id=\"page-title\"><div>Faculty Directory</div>Prem Kumar</h1><div id=\"faculty-profile-left\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"../../../images/research-and-faculty/directory/kumar-prem.jpg\"/><p class=\"title\">Professor of Electrical Engineering and Computer Science and Physics</p><p class=\"title\">Director of Center for Photonic Communication and Computing</p><h2>Contact</h2>2145 Sheridan Road<br/>Tech Room M392<br/>Evanston, IL 60208-3109<br/><br/><a class=\"phone_link\" href=\"tel://847-491-4128\"><span class=\"phone_link_verbose\">847-491-4128</span></a><a class=\"mail_link\" href=\"mailto:kumarp@northwestern.edu\">Email <span>Prem&#160;Kumar</span></a><h2 class=\"sites-header\">Website</h2><p><a href=\"http://www.ece.northwestern.edu/~kumarp/\" target=\"_blank\">Prem Kumar's Homepage</a></p><p><a href=\"http://cpcc.northwestern.edu/\" target=\"_blank\">Center for Photonic Communication and Computing</a></p><p><a href=\"http://www.eecs.northwestern.edu/~kumarp/research.html\" target=\"_blank\">Current Research</a></p><hr/><h2>Centers</h2><p>Center for Photonic Communication and Computing</p><hr/><h2>Departments</h2><p><a href=\"http://eecs.northwestern.edu\" target=\"_blank\">Electrical Engineering and Computer Science</a></p></div><div id=\"faculty-profile-right\"><h2>Education</h2><p>Ph.D. Physics, State University of New York at Buffalo, Buffalo, NY, 1980</p>\r\n<p>M.Sc. Physics, Indian Institute of Technology, Kanpur, India, 1976</p>\r\n<p>B.Sc. Physics, University of Delhi, Delhi, India, 1974</p><br/><h2>Research Interests</h2><p><p><strong>Expert Areas</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Quantum communications and quantum information processing/computing</li>\r\n<li>Quantum sensing and imaging</li>\r\n<li>Fiber-optic communications</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p> <strong>Research</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Developing advanced photonic devices and systems for communication and computing</li>\r\n<li>Increasing technological speeds through optical systems</li>\r\n<li>Creating networks and devices that take advantage of quantum mechanics for highly secure information and networking</li>\r\n<li>Developing tools for generating, distributing, and ultrafast processing of quantum entanglement</li>\r\n<li>Using quantum light for precision measurements, sensing, and imaging</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p> </p></p><br/><h2>Selected Publications</h2><ul><li>Kim Fook Lee, Ying Tian, He Yang, Kimmo Mustonen, Amos Martinez, Qing Dai, Esko I. Kauppinen, John Malowicki, Prem Kumar, Zhipei Sun, \"<em>Photon-Pair Generation with a 100 nm Thick Carbon Nanotube Film</em>\", Advanced Materials, (2017)</li><li>Paritosh Manurkar, Nitin Jain, Prem Kumar, Gregory S. Kanter, \"<em>Reshaping of telecom band optical signals using programmable pump pulses</em>\", CLEO, (2017)</li><li>Michael Silver, Paritosh Manurkar, Yu Ping Huang, Carsten Langrock, Martin M. Fejer, Prem Kumar, Gregory S. Kanter, \"<em>Spectrally multiplexed upconversion detection with c-band pump and signal wavelengths</em>\", IEEE Photonics Technology Letters, (2017)</li><li>Paritosh Manurkar, Nitin Jain, Prem Kumar, Gregory S. Kanter, \"<em>Programmable optical waveform reshaping on a picosecond timescale</em>\", Optics Letters, (2017)</li><li>Paritosh Manurkar, Nitin Jain, Michael Silver, Yu Ping Huang, Carsten Langrock, Martin M. Fejer, Prem Kumar, Gregory S. Kanter, \"<em>Multidimensional mode-separable frequency conversion for high-speed quantum communication</em>\", Optica, (2016)</li><li>Samantha J. Nowierski, Neal N. Oza, Prem Kumar, Gregory S. Kanter, \"<em>Tomographic reconstruction of time-bin-entangled qudits</em>\", Physical Review A - Atomic, Molecular, and Optical Physics, (2016)</li><li>Dmitry V. Strekalov, Abijith S. Kowligy, Vesselin G. Velev, Gregory S. Kanter, Prem Kumar, Yu Ping Huang, \"<em>Phase matching for the optical frequency conversion processes in whispering gallery mode resonators</em>\", Journal of Modern Optics, (2016)</li><li>Timothy M. Rambo, Joseph B. Altepeter, Prem Kumar, G. Mauro D'Ariano, \"<em>Functional quantum computing</em>\", Physical Review A - Atomic, Molecular, and Optical Physics, (2016)</li></ul></div><div style=\"clear: both;\">&#160;</div></div>\r\n  \r\n<div id=\"back-to-top\"><a href=\"#top\">BACK TO TOP</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<footer class=\"cf\" role=\"contentinfo\"><div class=\"header-container cf\"><a href=\"http://www.northwestern.edu\" id=\"footer-logo\" target=\"_blank\">Northwestern Seal</a><div id=\"footer-links\"><p><sp