g and Computer Science</a></p></div><div id=\"faculty-profile-right\"><h2>Research Interests</h2><div class=\"cb_field\">\r\n<div id=\"cbfv_70\">\r\n<p>I am an Assistant Professor of Instruction in Electrical Engineering. Previously, I was a Lecturer in EECS, as well as a postdoc working in the Center for Engineering and Health. My work focuses on creating technologies to make patients' lives easier. I specialize in signal and image processing, machine learning, and circuit and system design.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"sectiontableentry2 cbft_editorta cb_form_line cbclearboth\" id=\"cbfr_66\">\r\n<p>As a graduate student, my work focused on detecting people's heart rate remotely without any contact. Currently, I am more focused on product development and lecturing than on research.</p>\r\n<label for=\"cbfv_66\" id=\"cblabcbfv_66\"></label><label for=\"cbfv_66\" id=\"cblabcbfv_66\"></label></div><br/></div><div style=\"clear: both;\">&#160;</div></div>\r\n  \r\n<div id=\"back-to-top\"><a href=\"#top\">BACK TO TOP</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<footer class=\"cf\" role=\"contentinfo\"><div class=\"header-container cf\"><a href=\"http://www.northwestern.edu\" id=\"footer-logo\" target=\"_blank\">Northwestern Seal</a><div id=\"footer-links\"><p><span class=\"footer-branding-element\">McCormick School of Engineering,</span>&#160;\r\n                        \r\n                        \r\n                        <span class=\"footer-branding-element\">Northwestern University</span></p><address>Technological Institute, 2145 Sheridan Road, Evanston, IL 60208</address><p class=\"contact-info white-single-arrow\"><a href=\"../../../contact/index.html\">view all contact info</a></p><ul><li><a href=\"../../../academics/apply.html\">Admissions</a></li><li><a href=\"../index.html\">Faculty Directory</a></li><li><a href=\"http://giving.northwestern.edu/node/2668\" target=\"_blank\">Give to McCormick</a></li><li><a href=\"../../../contact/maps.html\">Tech Room Finde