header\">Website</h2><p><a href=\"http://www.cs.northwestern.edu/~riesbeck/\" target=\"_blank\">Chris Riesbeck's Homepage</a></p><hr/><h2>Departments</h2><p><a href=\"http://eecs.northwestern.edu\" target=\"_blank\">Electrical Engineering and Computer Science</a></p><h2>Affiliations</h2><p><a href=\"http://ai.northwestern.edu\" target=\"_blank\">Master of Science in Artificial Intelligence</a></p><p><a href=\"http://mpd.northwestern.edu\" target=\"_blank\">Master of Science in Product Design and Development Management Program</a></p><hr/><p><a href=\"http://mccormick.northwestern.edu/docs/public_cv/Riesbeck-Christopher-CV.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Download CV</a></p></div><div id=\"faculty-profile-right\"><h2>Education</h2><p>Ph.D. Computer Science, Stanford University, Palo Alto, CA</p>\r\n<p>M.A. Computer Science, Stanford University, Palo Alto, CA</p>\r\n<p>B.A. Mathematics, Alfred University, Alfred, NY</p><br/><h2>Research Interests</h2><p><p>Agile software development. Technology-enabled educational reform. Experiential knowledge-based language understanding and reasoning.</p></p><br/><h2>Selected Publications</h2><ul><li>L Qiu, CK Riesbeck, \"<em>Human-in-the-Loop: A Feedback-Driven Model for Authoring Knowledge-Based Interactive ...</em>\", Journal of Educational Computing Research, (2008)</li><li>L Qiu, C Riesbeck, \"<em>An Incremental Model for Developing Educational Critiquing Systems: Experiences with the ...</em>\", Journal of Interactive Learning Research, (2008)</li></ul></div><div style=\"clear: both;\">&#160;</div></div>\r\n  \r\n<div id=\"back-to-top\"><a href=\"#top\">BACK TO TOP</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<footer class=\"cf\" role=\"contentinfo\"><div class=\"header-container cf\"><a href=\"http://www.northwestern.edu\" id=\"footer-logo\" target=\"_blank\">Northwestern Seal</a><div id=\"footer-links\"><p><span class=\"footer-branding-element\">McCormick School of Engineering,</span>&#160;\r\n                        \r\n                       