<div><div class=\"hover-container\"><form action=\"http://googlesearch.northwestern.edu/search\" id=\"web-search\" method=\"get\"><input name=\"site\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"mcc\"/><input name=\"client\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"mcc\"/><input name=\"output\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"xml_no_dtd\"/><input name=\"proxystylesheet\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"mcc2014\"/><input name=\"filter\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"0\"/><input autocomplete=\"off\" id=\"q\" name=\"q\" placeholder=\"Search this site\" type=\"search\"/></form></div></div></li><li id=\"top-nav-explore\"><a href=\"../../../explore/index.html\">Explore</a></li></ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h1 id=\"major-title\"><span class=\"header-container\"><a href=\"../../index.html\">Research and Faculty</a><span class=\"extraneous\">, McCormick School of Engineering, Northwestern University</span></span></h1>\r\n<div id=\"mobile-nav\">\r\n<div id=\"mobile-nav-handle\">\r\n<div id=\"inner\">SECTION MENU</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</header>\r\n<div id=\"container\">\r\n<div id=\"left-col\"><div id=\"section-nav-head\">IN THIS SECTION</div><nav><ul><li><a href=\"../../index.html\">Research and Faculty</a></li><li class=\"active expanded section\"><a href=\"../index.html\">Faculty Directory</a><ul><li class=\"index\"><a href=\"../index.html\">Faculty Directory</a></li><li><a href=\"../faculty-fellows.html\">Faculty Fellows</a></li></ul></li></ul></nav></div>\r\n<div id=\"main-content-wrap\">\r\n<div id=\"main-content\" role=\"main\"><h1 id=\"page-title\"><div>Faculty Directory</div>Peter Scheuermann</h1><div id=\"faculty-profile-left\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"../../../images/research-and-faculty/directory/scheuermann-peter.jpg\"/><p class=\"title\">Professor Emeritus of Electrical Engineering and Computer Science</p><h2>Contact</h2>2145 Sheridan Road<br/>Tech Room L452<br/>Evanston, IL 60208-3109<br/><br/><a class=\"phone_link\" href=\"tel://847-491-7141\"><span class=\"phone_link_verbose\">847-491-7141</span></a><a class=\"mail_link\" href=\"mailto:peters@ece.northwestern.edu\">Email <span>Peter&#160;Scheuermann</span></a><h2 class=\"sites-header\">Website</h2><p><a href=\"http://users.eecs.northwestern.edu/~peters/\" target=\"_blank\">Peter Scheuermann's Homepage</a></p><hr/><h2>Departments</h2><p><a href=\"http://eecs.northwestern.edu\" target=\"_blank\">Electrical Engineering and Computer Science</a></p><hr/><p><a href=\"http://mccormick.northwestern.edu/docs/public_cv/Scheuermann-Peter-CV.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Download CV</a></p></div><div id=\"faculty-profile-right\"><h2>Education</h2><p>Ph.D. Computer Science, State University of New York, Stony Brook, NY</p>\r\n<p>M.S. Computer Science, State University of New York, Stony Brook, NY</p>\r\n<p>B.S. Applied Mathematics/Physics, Tel-Aviv University, Tel-Aviv, Israel</p><br/><h2>Research Interests</h2><p><p>Physical database design; parallel I/O systems; distributed and federated database systems; web caching and replication; data mining; mobile computing</p></p><br/><h2>Selected Publications</h2><ul><li>Fan Zhou, Goce Trajcevski, Roberto Tamassia, Besim Avci, Ashfaq Khokhar, Peter Scheuermann, \"<em>Bypassing holes in sensor networks</em>\", Ad Hoc Networks, (2017)</li><li>Besim Avci, Goce Trajcevski, Roberto Tamassia, Peter Scheuermann, Fan Zhou, \"<em>Efficient detection of motion-trend predicates in wireless sensor networks</em>\", Computer Communications, (2017)</li><li>Mihai Maruseac, Gabriel Ghinita, Goce Trajcevski, Peter Scheuermann, \"<em>Privacy-preserving detection of anomalous phenomena in crowdsourced environmental sensing using fine-grained weighted voting</em>\", GeoInformatica, (2017)</li><li>Besim Avci, Goce Trajcevski, Peter Scheuermann, \"<em>Tracking uncertain shapes with probabilistic bounds in sensor networks</em>\", Advances in Databases and Information Systems - 20th East European Conference, ADBIS 2016, Proceedings, (2016)</li><li>Oliviu C. Ghica, Cristina Nita-Rotaru, Goce Trajcevski, Peter Scheuermann, \"<em>Security of electrostatic field persistent routing</em>\", Ad Hoc Networks, (2016)</li><li>Muhammed Mas Ud Hussain, Besim Avci, Goce Trajcevski, Peter Scheuermann, \"<em>Incorporating weather updates for public transportation users of recommendation systems</em>\", Proceedings - 2016 IEEE 17th International Conference on Mobile Data Management, IEEE MDM 2016, (2016)</li><li>Trajcevski, Goce; Dick, Robert P.; Yazji, Sausan; Scheuermann, Peter; Jin, Ruoming, \"<em>Efficient location aware intrusion detection to protect mobile devices</em>\", Personal and Ubiquitous Computing, (2014)</li><li>Trajcevski, Goce; Scheuermann, Peter; Sun, Xiling; Yaagoub, Anan; Chen, Hao, \"<em>P 2 EST: Parallelization philosophies for evaluating spatio-temporal queries</em>\", Proceedings of the 2nd ACM SIGSPATIAL International Workshop on Analytics for Big Geospatial Data, BigSpatial 2013, (2013)</li></ul></div><div style=\"clear: both;\">&#160;</div></div>\r\n  \r\n<div id=\"back-to-top\"><a href=\"#top\">BACK TO TOP</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<footer class=\"cf\" role=\"contentinfo\"><div class=\"header-container cf\"><a href=\"http://www.northwestern.edu\" id=\"footer-logo\" target=\"_blank\">Northwestern Seal</a><div id=\"footer-links\"><p><span class=\"footer-branding-element\">McCormick School of Engineering,</span>&#160;\r\n                        \r\n                        \r\n                        <span class=\"footer-branding-element\">Northwestern University</span></p><address>Technological Institute, 2145 Sheridan Road, Evanston, IL 60208</address><p class=\"contact-info white-single-arrow\"><a href=\"../../../contact/index.html\">view all contact info</a></p><ul><li><a href=\"../../../academics/apply.html\">Admissions</a></li><li><a href=\"../index.html\">Faculty Directory</a></li><li><a href=\"http://giving.northwestern.edu/node/2668\" target=\"_blank\">Give to McCormick</a></li><li><a href=\"../../../contact/maps.html\">Tech Room Finder / Maps</a></li><li><a href=