es and services for all parties</small></div><ul><li><a href=\"../../../about/departments-institutes.html#departments\">Academic Departments</a></li><li><a href=\"../../../offices-services/index.html#admin\">Administration, Finance, Facilities &amp; Planning</a></li><li><a href=\"../../../offices-services/index.html#alumni\">Alumni Relations &amp; Development</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.mccormick.northwestern.edu/career-development/index.html\">Career Development</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.mccormick.northwestern.edu/corporate-engagement/index.html\">Corporate Engagement</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.mccormick.northwestern.edu/services/index.html\">Customer Service Center</a></li><li><a href=\"../../../offices-services/index.html#faculty\">Faculty Affairs</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.mccormick.northwestern.edu/global/index.html\">Global Initiatives</a></li><li><a href=\"../../../offices-services/index.html#graduate\">Graduate Studies</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.mccormick.northwestern.edu/it-resources/index.html\">Information Technology</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.mccormick.northwestern.edu/marketing/index.html\">Marketing &amp; Communications</a></li><li><a href=\"../../../offices-services/index.html#advising\">McCormick Advising System</a></li><li><a href=\"../../../offices-services/index.html#dean\">Office of the Dean</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.mccormick.northwestern.edu/personal-development/index.html\">Personal Development</a></li><li><a href=\"../../../offices-services/index.html#research\">Research Offices</a></li><li><a href=\"../../../offices-services/index.html#undergraduate\">Undergraduate Engineering</a></li></ul></div></div></li><li id=\"nav-search\"><a class=\"icon-search-glass\" href=\"http://googlesearch.northwestern.edu/search?site=mcc&amp;client=mcc&amp;output=xml_no_dtd&amp;proxystylesheet=mcc2014&amp;filter=0\">web search</a><div><div class=\"hover-container\"><form action=\"http://googlesearch.northwestern.edu/search\" id=\"web-search\" method=\"get\"><input name=\"site\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"mcc\"/><input name=\"client\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"mcc\"/><input name=\"output\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"xml_no_dtd\"/><input name=\"proxystylesheet\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"mcc2014\"/><input name=\"filter\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"0\"/><input autocomplete=\"off\" id=\"q\" name=\"q\" placeholder=\"Search this site\" type=\"search\"/></form></div></div></li><li id=\"top-nav-explore\"><a href=\"../../../explore/index.html\">Explore</a></li></ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h1 id=\"major-title\"><span class=\"header-container\"><a href=\"../../index.html\">Research and Faculty</a><span class=\"extraneous\">, McCormick School of Engineering, Northwestern University</span></span></h1>\r\n<div id=\"mobile-nav\">\r\n<div id=\"mobile-nav-handle\">\r\n<div id=\"inner\">SECTION MENU</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</header>\r\n<div id=\"container\">\r\n<div id=\"left-col\"><div id=\"section-nav-head\">IN THIS SECTION</div><nav><ul><li><a href=\"../../index.html\">Research and Faculty</a></li><li class=\"active expanded section\"><a href=\"../index.html\">Faculty Directory</a><ul><li class=\"index\"><a href=\"../index.html\">Faculty Directory</a></li><li><a href=\"../faculty-fellows.html\">Faculty Fellows</a></li></ul></li></ul></nav></div>\r\n<div id=\"main-content-wrap\">\r\n<div id=\"main-content\" role=\"main\"><h1 id=\"page-title\"><div>Faculty Directory</div>Sara Owsley Sood </h1><div id=\"faculty-profile-left\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"../../../images/research-and-faculty/directory/sood-sara.jpg\"/><p class=\"title\">Associate Professor of Instruction</p><p class=\"title\">Chookaszian Family Teaching Professor</p><h2>Contact</h2>2145 Sheridan Road<br/>Ford Room 3-327<br/>Evanston, IL 60208-3109<br/><br/><a class=\"phone_link\" href=\"tel://847-491-5708\"><span class=\"phone_link_verbose\">847-491-5708</span></a><a class=\"mail_link\" href=\"mailto:sara.sood@northwestern.edu\">Email <span>Sara Owsley&#160;Sood </span></a><h2 class=\"sites-header\">Website</h2><p><a href=\"http://labfs.eecs.northwestern.edu/~sara/Site/Home.html\" target=\"_blank\">Sara Sood's website</a></p><p><a href=\"http://infolab.northwestern.edu/\" target=\"_blank\">Intelligent Information Lab</a></p><hr/><h2>Departments</h2><p><a href=\"http://eecs.northwestern.edu\" target=\"_blank\">Electrical Engineering and Computer Science</a></p><h2>Affiliations</h2><p><a href=\"http://ai.northwestern.edu\" target=\"_blank\">Master of Science in Artificial Intelligence</a></p></div><div id=\"faculty-profile-right\"><h2>Research Interests</h2><p>My work is focused on understanding the expression and impact of emotion in online communication. To this end, my recent work has been on systems to detect and analyze insults, profanity and personal attacks in online forums with a recent focus on the impact of anonymity on online communities. My work in the space of sentiment analysis has led me to explore a series of other related challenges including domain specificity and sentiment analysis through many models of emotion beyond positive/negative/neutral classification.</p><br/><h2>Significant Recognition</h2><ul><li>2010 Pomona College Wig Distinguished Professor Award for Excellence in Teaching</li></ul><br/><h2>Selected Publications</h2><ul><div class=\"text-content style_External_630_782\">\r\n<div class=\"style\">\r\n<p><strong><span>2014</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"paragraph_style_1\"><span class=\"style_1\">Koh, S., Gordon, A., Wienberg, C., Sood, S.O., Morley, S., and Burke, D.</span><a class=\"style_1\" href=\"http://labfs.eecs.northwestern.edu/%7Esara/Site/Publications.html\">Stroke Experiences in Weblogs: A Feasibility Study of Sex Differences.</a> <span class=\"style_1\">Accepted and in Publication Process - Journal of Medical Internet Research, 2014.<br/>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<br/>\r\n<p><strong><span>2013</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"paragraph_style_1\"><span class=\"style_1\">Omernick, Eli, and Sood, Sara Owsley.</span> <a class=\"style_1\" href=\"http://labfs.eecs.northwestern.edu/%7Esara/Site/Publications_files/anonymitySood.pdf\">The Impact of Anonymity in Online Communities.</a> <span class=\"style_1\">In Proceedings of the ASE/IEEE International Conference on Social Computing, September 2013.<br/>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<br/>\r\n<p><strong><span>2012</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"paragraph_style_1\"><span class=\"style_1\">Gordon, Andrew S., Wienberg, Christopher, and Sood, Sara Owsley.</span> <a class=\"style_1\" href=\"http://labfs.eecs.northwestern.edu/%7Esara/Site/Publications_files/SOCIALCOM-2012-updated.PDF\">Different Strokes of Different Folks.</a> <span class=\"style_1\">In proceedings of the International Conference on Social Computing, September 2012.<br/>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<br/>\r\n<p class=\"paragraph_style_1\"><span class=\"style_1\">Sood, Sara Owsley, Antin, Judd, and Churchill, Elizabeth F.</span> <a class=\"style_1\" href=\"http://labfs.eecs.northwestern.edu/%7Esara/Site/Publications_files/Sood_profanity_AAAI.pdf\">Using Crowdsourcing to Improve Profanity Detection.</a> <span class=\"style_1\">In proceedings of the AAAI Spring Symposium, Wisdom of the Crowd, March 2012.<br/>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<br/>\r\n<p class=\"paragraph_style_1\"><span class=\"style_1\">Sood, Sara Owsley, Antin, Judd, and Churchill, Elizabeth F.</span> <a class=\"style_1\" href=\"http://labfs.eecs.northwestern.edu/%7Esara/Site/Publications_files/chi_profanity.pdf\">Profanity use in online communities.</a> <span class=\"style_1\">In proceedings of ACM SIGCHI, May 2012.<br/>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<br/>\r\n<p class=\"paragraph_style_1\"><span class=\"style_1\">Sood, Sara Owsley, Churchill, Elizabeth F., and Antin, Judd.</span> <a class=\"style_1\" href=\"http://labfs.eecs.northwestern.edu/%7Esara/Site/Publications_files/JASIST_r1.pdf\">Automatic identification of personal insults on social news sites.</a> <span class=\"style_1\">In Journal of the American Society for Information Science and Technology (JASIST), 63(2): 270-285, 2012.<br/>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<br/>\r\n<p><strong><span>2011</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"paragraph_style_1\"><span class=\"style_1\">Gonzalez, Maribel, Lucy Vasserman, Sara Owsley Sood and Tzu-Yi Chen.</span> <a class=\"style_1\" href=\"http://labfs.eecs.northwestern.edu/%7Esara/Site/Publications_files/paysFinal.pdf\">Leveraging Existing Outreach Programs to Reach Underrepresented Minorities.</a> <span class=\"style_1\">Journal of Computing Sciences in Colleges: Vol. 26 Issue 4, April 2011 (pages 190-196).<br/>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"paragraph_style_1\"><span class=\"style_2\">&#160;</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span>2010</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"paragraph_style_1\"><span class=\"style_1\">Sood, Sara Owsley and Churchill, Elizabeth F.</span> <a class=\"style_1\" href=\"http://labfs.eecs.northwestern.edu/%7Esara/Site/Publications_files/SentimentSoodChurchillFinal.pdf\">Anger Management: Using Sentiment Analysis to Manage Online Communities.</a> <span class=\"style_1\">In proceedings of the Grace Hopper Celebration, 2010.<br/>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"paragraph_style_1\"><span class=\"style_2\">&#160;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"paragraph_style_1\"><span class=\"style_1\">Karaali, Gizem, Philip I. Choi, Sara Owsley Sood, and Eric B. Grosfils.</span> <a class=\"style_1\" href=\"http://services.bepress.com/numeracy/vol3/iss1/art4\" title=\"http://services.bepress.com/numeracy/vol3/iss1/art4\">Envisioning a Quantitative Studies Center: A Liberal Arts Perspective.</a> <span class=\"style_1\">Numeracy: Vol. 3: Iss. 1, Article 4, 2010.<br/>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<br/>\r\n<p><strong><span>2009</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"paragraph_style_1\"><span class=\"style_1\">Sood, Sara Owsley and Vasserman, Lucy.</span> <a class=\"style_1\" href=\"http://labfs.eecs.northwestern.edu/%7Esara/Site/Publications_files/sood_vasserman_icwsm09_final.pdf\" title=\"Publications_files/sood_vasserman_icwsm09_final.pdf\">ESSE: Exploring Mood on the Web.</a> <span class=\"style_1\">International Conference on Weblogs and Social Media Data, 2009.<br/>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"paragraph_style_1\"><span class=\"style_2\">&#160;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"paragraph_style_1\"><span class=\"style_1\">Sood, Sara Owsley and Vasilakos, Thanos.</span> <a class=\"style_1\" href=\"http://www.springer.com/computer/information+systems+and+applications/book/978-0-387-89023-4\">Digital Theater: Dynamic Theatre Spaces.</a> <span class=\"style_1\">In \"Handbook of Multimedia for Digital Entertainment and Arts\" edited by Borko Furht, Springer, 2009 (pages 423-446).<br/>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"paragraph_style_1\"><span class=\"style_2\">&#160;</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span>2008</span></strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"paragraph_style_1\"><span class=\"style_1\">Wensel, April and Sood, Sara Owsley.</span> <a class=\"style_1\" href=\"http://labfs.eecs.northwestern.edu/%7Esara/Site/Publications_files/smrc02-wensel.pdf\" title=\"Publications_files/smrc02-wensel.pdf\">VIBES: Visualizing Changing Emotional States in Personal Stories.</a> <span class=\"style_1\">ACM MultiMedia - Story Representation, Mechanism and Context, 2008.<br/>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"paragraph_style_1\"><span class=\"style_2\">&#160;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"paragraph_style_1\"><span class=\"style_1\">Sood, Sara Owsley.</span> <a class=\"style_1\" href=\"http://labfs.eecs.northwestern.edu/%7Esara/Site/Publications_files/Sood-Buzz-IJART.pdf\" title=\"Publications_files/Sood-Buzz-IJART.pdf\">Buzz: Mining and Presenting Interesting Stories.</a> <span class=\"style_1\">The International Journal of Art and Technology V1 N1, 2008.<br/>\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"paragraph_style_1\"><span class=\"style_2\">&#160;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"paragraph_style_1\"><span class=\"style_1\">Sood, Sara Owsley.</span> <a class=\"style_1\" href=\"http://labfs.eecs.northwestern.edu/%7Esara/Site/Publications_files/Sood_Emotional_Comput