id=\"web-search\" method=\"get\"><input name=\"site\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"mcc\"/><input name=\"client\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"mcc\"/><input name=\"output\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"xml_no_dtd\"/><input name=\"proxystylesheet\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"mcc2014\"/><input name=\"filter\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"0\"/><input autocomplete=\"off\" id=\"q\" name=\"q\" placeholder=\"Search this site\" type=\"search\"/></form></div></div></li><li id=\"top-nav-explore\"><a href=\"../../../explore/index.html\">Explore</a></li></ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h1 id=\"major-title\"><span class=\"header-container\"><a href=\"../../index.html\">Research and Faculty</a><span class=\"extraneous\">, McCormick School of Engineering, Northwestern University</span></span></h1>\r\n<div id=\"mobile-nav\">\r\n<div id=\"mobile-nav-handle\">\r\n<div id=\"inner\">SECTION MENU</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</header>\r\n<div id=\"container\">\r\n<div id=\"left-col\"><div id=\"section-nav-head\">IN THIS SECTION</div><nav><ul><li><a href=\"../../index.html\">Research and Faculty</a></li><li class=\"active expanded section\"><a href=\"../index.html\">Faculty Directory</a><ul><li class=\"index\"><a href=\"../index.html\">Faculty Directory</a></li><li><a href=\"../faculty-fellows.html\">Faculty Fellows</a></li></ul></li></ul></nav></div>\r\n<div id=\"main-content-wrap\">\r\n<div id=\"main-content\" role=\"main\"><h1 id=\"page-title\"><div>Faculty Directory</div>Qi Zhu</h1><div id=\"faculty-profile-left\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"../../../images/research-and-faculty/directory/zhu-qi.jpg\"/><p class=\"title\">Associate Professor of Electrical Engineering and Computer Science</p><h2>Contact</h2>2145 Sheridan Road<br/>Tech Room L454<br/>Evanston, IL 60208-3109<br/><br/><a class=\"mail_link\" href=\"mailto:qzhu@northwestern.edu\">Email <span>Qi&#160;Zhu</span></a><h2 class=\"sites-header\">Website</h2><p><a href=\"http://users.eecs.northwestern.edu/~qzhu/\" target=\"_blank\">Qi Zhu's Homepage</a></p><p><a href=\"http://zhulab.eecs.northwestern.edu/\" target=\"_blank\">IDEAS - Design Automation of Intelligent Systems Lab</a></p><hr/><h2>Departments</h2><p><a href=\"http://eecs.northwestern.edu\" target=\"_blank\">Electrical Engineering and Computer Science</a></p><hr/><p><a href=\"http://mccormick.northwestern.edu/docs/public_cv/Zhu-Qi-CV.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Download CV</a></p></div><div id=\"faculty-profile-right\"><h2>Education</h2><p>Ph.D. Electrical Engineering &amp; Computer Science, University of California, Berkeley</p>\r\n<p>B.E. Computer Science, Tsinghua University, <span class=\"_Xbe\">Beijing Shi, China</span></p>\r\n<p>&#160;</p><br/><h2>Research Interests</h2><p>My research interests include design automation of intelligent cyber-physical systems and Internet-of-Things applications, cyber-physical security, energy-efficient CPS, and system-on-chip design.</p>\r\n<p><span>Recent work in my group has been focusing on system level synthesis, optimization and modeling methodologies for intelligent cyber-physical systems. We are particularly interested in addressing&#160;</span><em>timing, heterogeneity, security and energy challenges</em><span>&#160;in CPS design and operation.</span></p>\r\n<span></span><br/><h2>Selected Publications</h2><ul><li>Tianshu Wei, Mohammad Atiqul Islam, Shaolei Ren, Qi Zhu, \"<em>Co-scheduling of datacenter and HVAC loads in mixed-use buildings</em>\", 2016 7th International Green and Sustainable Computing Conference, IGSC 2016, (2017)</li><li>Qi Zhu, Srikrishnan Venkataraman, Chunfei Ye, Arun Chandrasekhar, \"<em>Package design challenges and optimizations in density efficient (Intel&#157; Xeon&#157; processor D) SoC</em>\", 2016 IEEE Electrical Design of Advanced Packaging and Systems Symposium, EDAPS 2016, (2017)</li><li>Bowen Zheng, Chung Wei Lin, Hengyi Liang, Shinichi Shiraishi, Wenchao Li, Qi Zhu, \"<em>Delay-Aware Design, Analysis and Verification of Intelligent Intersection Management</em>\", 2017 IEEE International Conference on Smart Computing, SMARTCOMP 2017, (2017)</li><li>Tiansong Cui, Shuang Chen, Yanzhi Wang, Qi Zhu, Shahin Nazarian, Massoud Pedram, \"<em>An optimal energy co-scheduling framework for smart buildings</em>\", Integration, the VLSI Journal, (2017)</li><li>Tianshu Wei, Yanzhi Wang, Qi Zhu, \"<em>Deep Reinforcement Learning for Building HVAC Control</em>\", Proceedings of the 54th Annual Design Automation Conference 2017, DAC 2017, (2017)</li><li>Qi Zhu, Hengyi Liang, Licong Zhang, Debayan Roy, Wenchao Li, Samarjit Chakraborty, \"<em>Extensibility-Driven Automotive In-Vehicle Architecture Design</em>\", Proceedings of the 54th Annual Design Automation Conference 2017, DAC 2017, (2017)</li><li>Xiaodao Chen, Yuchen Zhou, Hong Zhou, Chaowei Wan, Qi Zhu, Wenchao Li, Shiyan Hu, \"<em>Analysis of production data manipulation attacks in petroleum cyber-physical systems</em>\", 2016 IEEE/ACM International Conference on Computer-Aided Design, ICCAD 2016, (2016)</li><li>Bowen Zheng, Chung Wei Lin, Huafeng Yu, Hengyi Liang, Qi Zhu, \"<em>CONVINCE</em>\", 2016 IEEE/ACM International Conference on Computer-Aided Design, ICCAD 2016, (2016)</li></ul></div><div style=\"clear: both;\">&#160;</div></div>\r\n  \r\n<div id=\"back-to-top\"><a href=\"#top\">BACK TO TOP</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<footer class=\"cf\" role=\"contentinfo\"><div class=\"header-container cf\"><a href=\"http://www.northwestern.edu\" id=\"footer-logo\" target=\"_blank\">Northwestern Seal</a><div id=\"footer-links\"><p><span class=\"footer-branding-element\">McCormick School of Engineering,</span>&#160;\r\n                        \r\n                        \r\n                        <span class=\"footer-branding-element\">Northwestern University</span></p><address>Technological Institute, 2145 Sheridan Road, Evanston, IL 60208</address><p class=\"contact-info white-single-arrow\"><a href=\"../../../contact/index.html\">view all contact info</a></p><ul><li><a href=\"../../../academics/apply.html\">Admissions</a></li><li><a href=\"../index.html\">Faculty Directory</a></li><li><a href=\"http://giving.northwestern.edu/node/2668\" target=\"_blank\">Give to McCormick</a></li><li><a href=\"../../../contact/maps.html\">Tech Room Finder / Maps</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.mccormick.northwestern.edu/faculty-staff-resources/safety-emergency-information/index.html\">Emergency Information</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.northwestern.edu\" target=\"_blank\">Northwestern Home</a></li><li><a href=\"http://www.mccormick.northwestern.edu/offices-services/index.html#lost-and-found\" target=\"_blank\">Tech Lost and Found</a></li></ul></div><div id=\"footer-icons\"><div id=\"footer-icon-set1\"><a class=\"icon-twitter iconset-footer\" href=\"http://twitter.com/NorthwesternEng\" target=\"_blank\">McCormick on twitter</a><a class=\"icon-facebook iconset-footer\" href=\"http://facebook.com/northwesternengineering\" target=\"_blank\">McCormick on facebook</a><a class=\"icon-google iconset-footer\" href=\"https://plus.google.com/112338659769568952865/posts\" target=\"_blank\">McCormick on google</a></div><div id=\"footer-icon-set2\"><a class=\"icon-linkedin iconset-footer\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/groups?gid=51604\" target=\"_blank\">McCormick on linkedin</a><a class=\"icon-rss iconset-footer\" href=\"http://mccormick.northwestern.edu/rss/mcc.xml\" target=\"_blank\">McCormick on rss</a><a class=\"icon-youtube iconset-footer\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/NUMcCormick\" target=\"_blank\">McCormick on youtube</a></div></div></div><div id=\"footer-copyright\"><div class=\"header-container\">\r\n                     &#169; \r\n                    \r\n                    \r\n                    \r\n                    \r\n                    2018 Robert R. McCormick School of Engineering and Applied Science, Northwestern University \r\n                    \r\n                    \r\n                    \r\n                    \r\n                    <a href=\"http://www.northwestern.edu/disclaimer.html\" target=\"_blank\">Disclaimer</a></div></div></footer>\r\n\r\n   <!--[if lte IE 8]>\n      <script src=\"/js/selectivizr.min.js\"></script>\n    <![endif]-->\r\n    <!--[if lte IE 9]>\n      <script src=\"/js/media.match.min.js\"></script>\n      <script src=\"/js/rem.js\"></script>\n    <![endif]-->\r\n    <!--[if lte IE 10]>\n        <script src=\"/js/placeholders.js\"></script>\n    <![endif]-->\r\n\r\n\r\n\n<script src=\"/js/jquery/jquery.fitvids.js\"></script>\n<script src=\"/js/breakpoints.js\" type=\"text/javascript\"></script>\n<script src=\"/js/modernizr.js\" type=\"text/javascript\"></script>\n<script src=\"/js/jquery/jquery-slick-1.3.6.js\" type=\"text/javascript\"></script>\n \r\n\r\n<script>\n  var mccdevSites = [\"mccormick-dev.tech.northwestern.edu/mechanical\", \"mccormick-dev.tech.northwestern.edu/civil-environmental\",\"mccormick-dev.tech.northwestern.edu/materials-science\",\"mccormick-dev.tech.northwestern.edu/biomedical\",\"mccormick-dev.tech.northwestern.edu/chemical-biological\",\"mccormick-dev.tech.northwestern.edu/industrial\",\"mccormick-dev.tech.northwestern.edu/applied-math\",\"mccormick-dev.tech.northwestern.edu/eecs\"];\n  var mccSites = [\"mccormick.northwestern.edu/mechanical\", \"mccormick.northwestern.edu/civil-environmental\",\"mccormick.northwestern.edu/materials-science\",\"mccormick.northwestern.edu/biomedical\",\"mccormick.northwestern.edu/chemical-biological\",\"mccormick.northwestern.edu/industrial\",\"mccormick.northwestern.edu/applied-math\",\"mccormick.northwestern.edu/eecs\"];\n  var mccdevProgramSites = [\"mccormick-dev.tech.northwestern.edu/program-base\",\"mccormick-dev.tech.northwestern.edu/analytics\",\"mccormick-dev.tech.northwestern.edu/biotechnology\", \"mccormick-dev.tech.northwestern.edu/engineering-management\", \"mccormick-dev.tech.northwestern.edu/information-technology\", \"mccormick-dev.tech.northwestern.edu/robotics\", \"mccormick-dev.tech.northwestern.edu/project-management\"